# This conky requires mpd+ncmpcpp for the MPD display and yaourt to be able to check for updates in the AUR repo
# The font needed for the icons is Tamsynmod. For some reason the ram icon didn't work for me (it used to), so I created an icon for it (ram.xbm)

short_units yes
background yes
out_to_console yes
out_to_x no
# Update interval in seconds
update_interval 0.75

TEXT
